SUMMARY: DELIVERY OPTIONS: The webshop provides two delivery methods for Croatia: DPD home delivery and BOX NOW parcel locker delivery. PRICING: DPD home delivery is priced at 4 EUR. BOX NOW parcel locker delivery costs 2 EUR. No free shipping threshold is mentioned. DELIVERY TIME: DPD delivery takes an average of 2-3 days for continental Croatia, while BOX NOW takes 1-2 days. Delivery to islands may take longer for both services. NOTABLE FEATURES: The website does not mention options for express delivery, weekend delivery, cash on delivery (COD), or specific policies for bulky items. In-store pickup is not offered as a delivery method for online orders. WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: The shipping information is easy to find on a dedicated 'Dostava' page but lacks comprehensive details.
